# Playwright 浏览器路径配置（可选）
# 不设则按 scripts/playwright-browser.mjs 的候选顺序自动查找
# （系统 Chrome → Playwright chromium 缓存 → playwright 默认）
#
# 指定系统 Chrome：
# PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSER=C:/Program Files/Google/Chrome/Application/chrome.exe
#
# 或指定 Playwright chromium（避免污染系统 Chrome 用户数据）：
# PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSER=C:/Users/No'mi'l/AppData/Local/ms-playwright/chromium-1217/chrome-win64/chrome.exe
